# awc-cli

> cli for https://server.ari-web.xyz/ using https://ari-web.xyz/gh/awc

# configuration

config is done through environement variables :

-   `INSTANCE` -- the server instance
-   `KEY` -- the server instance key
-   `ADMIN_CLR` -- admin ANSI colour
